description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a proactive, dynamic, self-motivated nurse with experience in respiratory care. The successful applicant will assess and treat patients referred with chronic respiratory disease. This will involve performing oxygen assessments, reviewing patients referred to our service for admission avoidance and running clinics for management of chronic respiratory conditions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ideally you will have experience of both community and secondary care respiratory patient management. Additionally, you will also be fundamental in providing and supporting the pulmonary rehabilitation services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The team you would be joining are highly motivated, receptive to change and dedicated to providing a high standard of nursing care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
